name: Jungle Torch
tag_list: seo, social-media, social-media-monitoring, seo-dashboard, linking, link-strategy, key-word-analysis
overview: Jungle Torch gives any company with a website a comprehensive view of their website position as it relates to SEO. Furthermore, it identifies crucial pieces of information that are not available anywhere else in the SEO world. In addition, Jungle Torch provides crucial data on social media and can determine who is saying what about a particular company good or bad. This information is of crucial importance to any company doing business on the web or agencys ervicing various accounts.
